OL,3,CFarage says Reform would evict all
OL,4,Cforeign nationals from social housing
OL,6,FReform UK leader Nigel Farage has said
OL,7,Fhe would evict all foreign nationals
OL,8,Ffrom social housing if the party was
OL,9,Fin power, claiming Britain is
OL,10,Fcurrently a "two tier state against
OL,11,Fwhite people".
OL,13,FThe MP for Clacton has faced criticism
OL,14,Fover his first Substack essay, drawing
OL,15,Fcomparisons to a modern-day Enoch
OL,16,FPowell.
OL,18,FPublished on Sunday morning, Farage in
OL,19,Fhis essay repeated his vow to "repeal
OL,20,Fthe Equality Act" under a Reform
OL,21,Fgovernment.
OL,26,@rD@MOUsD@MO]{D@_OU|D@QO]
