OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1781525476
OL,3,CFarage says Reform would evict all
OL,4,Cforeign nationals from social housing
OL,6,FReferring to the murder of student
OL,7,FHenry Nowak, who was handcuffed by
OL,8,Fpolice as he lay dying after his
OL,9,Fkiller, Vickrum Digwa, claimed to have
OL,10,Fbeen the victim of a racist attack,
OL,11,FFarage claimed the "British state is
OL,12,Fno longer working for everyone in this
OL,13,Fcountry".
OL,15,FHis essay, titled 'Britain Is A Two
OL,16,FTier State ` Against White People',
OL,17,Fmakes a series of points about how he
OL,18,Fclaims "there is nothing fair about
OL,19,Fthe way white people have been treated
OL,20,Fby their governments".
OL,26,@sD@TOUuD@HO]zD@HOU|D@UO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
