OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1781525476
OL,3,CFarage says Reform would evict all
OL,4,Cforeign nationals from social housing
OL,6,FHousing, healthcare, education,
OL,7,Fpolicing, the military and the
OL,8,Fworkplace are all listed as being
OL,9,Fadversely affected by what he
OL,10,Fdescribes as "deeply anti-white
OL,11,Fracism".
OL,13,F"Across public and economic life, the
OL,14,Fpower of the Government has been
OL,15,Fbrought to bear on tackling
OL,16,F'inequalities', in a narrow and
OL,17,Fspecific sense," Farage wrote.
OL,26,@rD@NOUsD@GO]uD@AOUyD@PO]
