OL,3,CFarage says Reform would evict all
OL,4,Cforeign nationals from social housing
OL,6,F"Anything which is seen to
OL,7,Fdisadvantage a minority group is
OL,8,Fcracked down on. Anything which
OL,9,Fbenefits a minority and damages the
OL,10,FWhite British is likely to be left
OL,11,Falone."
OL,13,FOn the topic of housing, he said that
OL,14,Fduring the last century, "rules which
OL,15,Fgave priority to local people and ties
OL,16,Fto the area were stripped away".
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@GO]vD@ZOUxD@_O]
