OL,3,CFarage says Reform would evict all
OL,4,Cforeign nationals from social housing
OL,6,FHe said that, under a Reform
OL,7,Fgovernment, foreign nationals in
OL,8,Fsocial housing would be given a three-
OL,9,Fmonth grace period to relocate to
OL,10,Fprivate rented accommodation, or lose
OL,11,Ftheir right to remain in the country
OL,12,Fand be liable for deportation.
OL,14,FFarage wrote that he was launching the
OL,15,FSubstack so he could set out his views
OL,16,Fin his own words to avoid them being
OL,17,F"twisted and misrepresented,"
OL,18,Fpromising to publish a "long essay"
OL,19,Feach month.
OL,26,@yD@AOUyD@]O]zD@XOUzD@cO]
