OL,3,CFarage says Reform would evict all
OL,4,Cforeign nationals from social housing
OL,6,FAppearing on Sky News, Culture
OL,7,FSecretary Lisa Nandy said Farage
OL,8,F"should take his nasty hate and anger
OL,9,Fand division somewhere else frankly".
OL,11,F"I think people want hope," she added.
OL,13,F"They don't want more anger, they
OL,14,Fdon't want more division, they don't
OL,15,Fwant more hate, and I wish he'd just
OL,16,Ftake it somewhere else."
OL,18,FResponding to Farage's essay, Liberal
OL,19,FDemocrat leader Sir Ed Davey described
OL,20,Fhim as "the Enoch Powell of the social
OL,21,Fmedia age".
OL,26,@pD@AOUqD@dO]sD@AOUsD@[O]uD@AOUxD@XO]|D@
OL,26,AHOU}D@JO]
