OL,3,CFarage says Reform would evict all
OL,4,Cforeign nationals from social housing
OL,6,FPowell made a speech widely remembered
OL,7,Ffor the phrase "rivers of blood" in
OL,8,F1968, when he was a Conservative
OL,9,Fshadow minister, which was blamed for
OL,10,Finflaming racial tensions at the time.
OL,12,F"He's trying to excuse racist disorder
OL,13,Fand violence against police officers,"
OL,14,FDavey said. "He's pushing the politics
OL,15,Fof grievance and division that goes
OL,16,Ftotally against our fundamental
OL,17,FBritish values of tolerance and
OL,18,Fdecency.
OL,26,@oD@POUoD@`O]tD@AOUuD@fO]vD@MOU
